  "text": "Myeloid cell-specific promoter. Myeloid specific promoters that have been used to date in humanized mice have targeted specific subsets of myeloid cells. An HLA-DR-specific promoter has been characterized in NOD/SCID mice as a way of transducing human antigen presenting cells in humanized mice. [CITATION_1] Platelet-specific promoter integrin aIIb has been shown to be active in human CD34",
